documentation.content: Vacation Request - BPMN MIWG demo for 2022

mail_subject.#text: Your Vacation Request ${SYS.PROCESSINSTANCE_ID} was refused automatically

ns1:literalExpression.ns1:text:
Hi Current Vacation Status.name,

 

Your vacation request from date(From) to date(To) was declined for the following reason: Reason 

 Best regards

 

This is an automated message generated by the vacation system.

input_parameters.source:
= "

Hi  " + Current Vacation Status.name + ",

 

Your vacation request from " + From + " to " + To + " was declined for the following reason: " + Reason + "

 

Best regards

 

This is an automated message generated by the vacation system.

"

description.#text: This is a demonstration scenario for automation and shows how vacation request could be handled using business rules.

Task.Description: The automatic approval resulted in "Manual Validation Required". Please check the Vacation Request and approve or decline it.

extension_elements.triso_documentation: Vacation Request process for EU-Rent. This process will first try to apply the company automated rules and will offer a manual approval if the manager discretion should be taken.
